00:30:25,100 --> 00:30:27,860
 And think about it.

552
00:30:27,860 --> 00:30:30,180
 In the great scheme of things,

553
00:30:30,180 --> 00:30:35,180
 God does not really care about your earthly achievement.

554
00:30:35,180 --> 00:30:40,060
 What He cares is how you manage it to glorify Him.

555
00:30:40,060 --> 00:30:43,440
 How you build your life on the word of God,

556
00:30:43,440 --> 00:30:44,780
 in obedience to Him.

557
00:30:44,780 --> 00:30:47,760
 That is what matters at the end of the day.

558
00:30:47,760 --> 00:30:54,380
 You are God's steward and trusted with all sorts of things.

559
00:30:54,380 --> 00:30:58,220
 How are you managing it?

560
00:30:59,500 --> 00:31:03,180
 If God calls you to give an account today,

