00:32:08,300 --> 00:32:12,200
 If you go to a funeral, if you go to a funeral,

582
00:32:12,200 --> 00:32:15,320
 well, I mean, it's not a nice thing to say,

583
00:32:15,320 --> 00:32:17,620
 but you should go to funerals more.

584
00:32:17,620 --> 00:32:20,300
 At 10 funerals.

585
00:32:20,300 --> 00:32:22,180
 You know why?

586
00:32:22,180 --> 00:32:26,500
 Because there's a part in the funeral service,

587
00:32:26,500 --> 00:32:29,300
 there's a part called eulogy.

588
00:32:29,300 --> 00:32:33,100
 Eulogy means speak good, right?

589
00:32:33,100 --> 00:32:34,920
 Speak good, it's a Greek word.

590
00:32:34,920 --> 00:32:37,620
 Speak good of a person, right?

591
00:32:37,620 --> 00:32:41,040
 Eulogy is, you know, reciting the history

592
00:32:41,040 --> 00:32:43,320
 or remembering the history of someone,

593
00:32:43,320 --> 00:32:46,440
 the deceased family member.

594
00:32:46,440 --> 00:32:49,300
 All the eulogies I've heard

595
00:32:51,260 --> 00:32:56,260
 have nothing to do with the deceased achievements.

596
00:32:56,260 --> 00:33:00,820
 Nobody will come up to the podium in the funeral service

597
00:33:00,820 --> 00:33:04,300
 and say, "Oh, he got a lot of money, you know what?

598
00:33:04,300 --> 00:33:05,700
 "He got a lot of investment.

599
00:33:05,700 --> 00:33:08,580
 "He's so great in terms of money.

600
00:33:08,580 --> 00:33:12,340
 "Look at how many figures he has in the bank account."

601
00:33:12,340 --> 00:33:14,260
 Nobody will say anything like that.

602
00:33:14,260 --> 00:33:17,140
 Most of the eulogies will talk about

603
00:33:17,140 --> 00:33:18,540
 the character of the person.

604
00:33:19,820 --> 00:33:23,060
 How he has been a blessing to other people.

605
00:33:23,060 --> 00:33:28,620
 The family, the community, the neighborhood, right?

606
00:33:28,620 --> 00:33:31,500
 The church, his spiritual life.

607
00:33:31,500 --> 00:33:36,200
 Most of the things mentioned in the eulogies

608
00:33:36,200 --> 00:33:39,520
 are those things, the spiritual things, so to speak.

609
00:33:39,520 --> 00:33:42,100
 Your relationship with God

610
00:33:42,100 --> 00:33:45,100
 and your relationship with other people.

