00:33:47,820 --> 00:33:52,780
 or you are loving other people just as God loves them

613
00:33:52,780 --> 00:33:54,380
 and you try your best to do it,

614
00:33:54,380 --> 00:33:57,500
 those are the things going to the account.

615
00:33:57,500 --> 00:34:03,060
 Those are the things going to God's record of your life.

616
00:34:03,060 --> 00:34:06,220
 Don't lose that focus.

