00:34:50,380 --> 00:34:56,580
 And I pray, I pray that in times of blessing,

629
00:34:56,580 --> 00:34:57,700
 we do not forget you.

630
00:34:57,700 --> 00:35:01,900
 We thank you, we praise you.

631
00:35:01,900 --> 00:35:06,340
 And in times of crisis, we don't forget you,

632
00:35:06,340 --> 00:35:11,680
 knowing that you are our rock and you are our salvation.

633
00:35:13,020 --> 00:35:16,580
 Thank you for your deliverance, thank you for your healing,

634
00:35:16,580 --> 00:35:21,540
 thank you for your blessing that we enjoy.

635
00:35:21,540 --> 00:35:26,540
 So in times of crisis, help us to focus on you

636
00:35:26,540 --> 00:35:29,180
 because in the end of the days,

